    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "I'm Beruka, an assassin from Nohr. Need me for some missions? Fine. I'll take the job.",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "Order of Heroes—hmm, I bet that's just a fancy label for a group of assassins.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "My liege is Lady Camilla. She took me under her wing. So I'm going to protect her at all costs.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I'll always follow your instructions in a mission. I can read your lips from all the way across the battlefield.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I need the strongest weapon I can get, but I don't know what that is in this realm. Keep your eyes peeled.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I keep my weapons in top shape. So don't sneak up on me while I'm sharpening them, all right?",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I'm on a mission to deliver a critical message. Hello... from <Friend Name>. Mission complete.",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "To face me is death.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Time for a new objective...",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "...",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "More power? Good. I'll need it.",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "<Player Name>... I am glad to see you are still alive. Why am I glad? ...I don't know. I am not obligated to you. You are not my liege—we have no contractual arrangement. However, I...worry about your well-being. Presumably because of your irreplaceable abilities. Assassins like myself do not get emotionally attached, so I'm sure it's your abilities that concern me. ",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
